    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>In nomine Patris et Filii et Spiritus Sancti. Anno Deo propicio pontificatus
                        domni nostri <persName key="#Uncertain_tradition #Popes" ref="#people/2137"
                            >Benedicti</persName> summi pontificis et universalis <rs key="#Popes"
                            >pape</rs> in apostolica sacratissima beati Petri apostoli Domini sede
                        tertio sitque imperante domno ... a Deo coronato pacifico magno <rs
                            key="#Emperor/king">imperatore</rs> anno ..., die ...septimo mense
                        genuarii, indictione quarta... <persName key="#Priests #Abbots #Monks"
                            ref="#people/1581">Vitalis</persName> per divinam misericordiam <rs
                            key="#Priests">presbiter</rs>, <rs key="#Monks">monachus</rs> et <rs
                            key="#Abbots">abbas</rs>
                        <rs key="#Monasteries">monasterii</rs>
                        <orgName ref="#juridical_persons/1460"
                            key="#Fundi #Fiscal_property #Outflow #Allocation_to_individuals">Sancte
                            semperque Dei genitricis Marie que vocatur in <placeName
                                ref="#places/4179">Pomposia</placeName></orgName>, ... eiusdem
                        monasterii, uti nobis in Dei nomine ... et <persName><name ref="Paulus"
                                >Paulus</name></persName> filio meo seu ... habuerimus liceat nobis
                        dare ...cum erit designatum ... concedistis et largistis in annos
                        advenientes sexaginta, <rs key="#Fundi">fundum</rs> qui vocatur de
                            <placeName
                            key="#Fundi #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Allocation_to_individuals"
                                ><geogName
                                key="#Fundi #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Allocation_to_individuals"
                                ref="#estates/2463">Anlega</geogName></placeName> ... monasterii
                        vestri ... qui vocabatur Dragoli cum ... <rs key="#Fines">territorio</rs>
                        <placeName key="#Fines" ref="#places/3513"><geogName key="#Fines"
                                ref="#estates/2424">Faventino</geogName></placeName>, <rs
                            key="#Plebs">plebe</rs>
                        <orgName key="#Plebs" ref="#juridical_persons/3610">Sancti Stefani in
                                <placeName ref="#places/3586">Teguria</placeName></orgName> ...
                        supra legitur. Hec omnia habendum, tenendum, ... annos advenientes sexaginta
                        ... sicut supra legitur. Ita tamen ut ... aut ipso vestro sucessori tibi
                        predicto abbas ... singulis quibusque anni omni marcio mense ... que supra
                        legitur, idest <rs key="#Rent_in_money">in arientum denarios Venetos</rs>
                        ... Quam vero paginam <persName key="#Tabellio"><name ref="Petrus"
                                >Petrus</name></persName> in Dei nomine <rs key="#Tabellio"
                            >tabellio</rs> huius civitatis <placeName ref="#places/594"
                            >Ravenne</placeName> scribere rogavimus in qua et nos ... unus alterius
                        pariter contradimus, sub die, mense et indictione quarta...Signum manus mea
                        supradicta <persName><name ref="Atta">Atia</name></persName> relicta quondam
                                <persName><name ref="Faraldus">Farualdi</name></persName> qui
                        vocabatur ...scripti petitricis ad omnia ut supra legitur ... Paulus filius
                        quondam Farualdi subscripsi et ... <persName key="#Witness"><name
                                ref="Iohannes">Iohannes</name></persName> filius <persName><name
                                ref="Ursicinus">Ursicini</name></persName> in hec peticione ut supra
                        legitur rogatus <rs key="#Witness">testis</rs> subscripsi. <persName><name
                                ref="Iohannes">Ioannes</name></persName> filius quondam
                                <persName><name ref="Laurentius">Laurentii</name></persName> ...
                                <persName><name ref="Deusdedit">Deusdedit</name></persName> filius
                        quondam <persName><name ref="Gregorius">Gregorii</name></persName> ... Ego
                        Petrus in Dei nomine tabellio Ravenne scriptor hanc paginam peticionis post
                        roborationem testium atque traditam complevi et absolvi. Notitiam testium
                        idest: Iohannes vir clarissimus filius Ursicini, Iohannes vir clarissimus
                        filius Laurentii, Deusdedit vir clarissimus filius quondam Gregorii.</ab>
                </div>
